[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "砂、砂、砂……どこもかしこも砂まみれ！\n砂漠の国だ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00756",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "日差しはキツいけど、思ったより暑くないわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00757",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "湿度が低いんだと思う。\n気候としては神聖国に近いかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00758",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "くんくん……なんかいい匂いがする！\nお肉の焼ける匂い！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00759",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "陽気な音楽もそこかしこから聞こえてくる……\nなるほど、獣人の楽園と呼ばれる島だけあるな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00760",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "うん、なんていうか……島全体が\nお祭りをしてる感じがする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00761",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ちょっと砂が多いのが気になるけど、\nなんかここにいるだけで、楽しくなってきちゃう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00762",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ふふっ、はしゃぐイザナちゃんもかわいいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00763",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "この島の獣人は、角付きも多いのね。\nなんだか親近感覚えちゃうかも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00764",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "享楽的な都というのは分かりました。\nとなると気になるのは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_00765",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "獣人Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "んだとこらぁ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_701_036_00766",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "獣人Ｂ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "やるってのかぁ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_702_036_00767",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……やはり、少々治安がよろしくないようですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_00768",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "獣人の商人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "皆さんベスティラへようこそ！\n獣人のお仲間もおりますな、ささ、こちらをどうぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_703_036_00769",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "おっきいヤシの実！　中身を飲むの？　美味しそう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00770",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あっ、それは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00771",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なに？　まずいものでも入ってたりするの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00772",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "いや。観光客に押し売りで法外な料金を請求する\n悪質な商人がベスティラでは散見されてな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00773",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "我々監察官も、本腰を入れて撲滅してやろうかと\n思っているんだが――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00774",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "獣人の商人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "っ！　しまった、こいつら監察官か！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_703_036_00775",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あ、逃げた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00776",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "さすが獣人、素早いですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00777",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "追いかける！？　今なら追いつけるって\nハンマーがささやいてる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00778",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "いや、いい。請求の現場を目撃したわけじゃないしな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00779",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "獣人のお姉さんＡ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あらお兄さん、かっこいい！\nこの後お茶しに行かない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_704_036_00780",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "むぅ、その……困る。\n好意はありがたいが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00781",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "獣人のお姉さんＢ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そちらの坊やもかわいいわね。\n食べちゃいたいくらい♪",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_705_036_00782",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "あ、あああ、あの、そのっ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00783",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "ティムを食べるだと……？\nそれ以上近づいてみろ。ただじゃおかないぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00784",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あなたがた、わたくしの連れに何かご用でして？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_00785",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "獣人のお姉さんＡ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "うっ……負けた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_704_036_00786",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "獣人のお姉さんＢ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "いいオトコだと思ったのにお手付き済かぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_705_036_00787",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "ララ、助かった。\n何やら誤解された気もするが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00788",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "別にわたくしは構いませんわ。それにしても\nあなたがた兄弟は女性に免疫がございませんのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_00789",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "錬金術と、ティムの病気を治すことだけを\n考えていたからな……我ながら、不甲斐ないものだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00790",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "僕も、家で寝てることが多かったから……\nドキドキしたぁ、いい匂いしてたなぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00791",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ベスティラの治安回復も大切だが、目下の任務は別……\n我々は仕事に向かうが、お前たちはどうする？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00792",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "えっと、可能ならベスティラの国王陛下と\nお話ししたいのですが……難しいでしょうか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00793",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "諸島同盟監察局のツテってすごいですよ～。\n会談ができないか確認してみますね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00794",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……エルス、これから行方不明事件について\n調べに行くのよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00795",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "その通りだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00796",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ここ最近、若い獣人の娘ばかりが行方不明になる……\nこれは営利誘拐の可能性がある。調査せねばならない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00797",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私もその調査、手伝わせてほしいんだけど。\n腕前のほどは、航海中に見せた通りよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00798",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（こういった事件には、九偉人が介入してくる可能性が\n　ある。キューンちゃんたちと接触したいんだよね）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00799",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "謁見はレスナたちに任せるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00800",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、分かった。こっちは任せて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00801",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そういうわけで、お願い。\n新入りだと思ってこき使ってくれて構わないから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00802",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "私では顔が割れていて、それが不都合な場合もある。\n協力を得られるのはありがたい。よろしく頼む",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00803",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "えへへ、私にも後輩ができるんですね～\nヴァレリアさん、よろしくお願いします！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00804",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 49,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
